channel.title: Error Loading Maps
channel.description:
Hey guys, I am working with a Pi at the moment and have been adding a button that allows you to change the interface. I have changed so much, it would take forever to go back and fix it all. After adding everything needed with no errors, this appears when I run the server.
[code]Error: loaderror Loading maps 96[/code]
I haven't really been dealing with the maps, any idea on what I messed up?
